text:
From the very dawn of Donald Trump’s presidential campaign, he remained clear about one platform: The man wants a wall. But if the devil is in the details, well then, there must be two of them, because as Seth Meyers points out on Wednesday’s “A Closer Look,” Trump seemingly has no idea as to how a border wall between Mexico and the U.S. would actually work. Will the wall be physical? See-through? Metaphorical? Magical? The Chris Hardwick-hosted NBC game show called The Wall ? Wait, wait, yeah, pick the TV show, it’s definitely that last one.
